t more stringent constraints to many of these evolution parameters are\nneeded in order to draw quantitative conclusions from population synthesis\nwork.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 19 Nov 2003 22:25:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-12-30"}
